        f"드라이버: <b>{_v54_escape(V74_DB_DRIVER)}</b>\n"
        f"주소: <code>{_v54_escape(v74_mask_database_url())}</code>\n"
        f"스키마: <code>{_v54_escape(V74_DB_SCHEMA)}</code>\n"
